2. **Grand Duchy of Lithuania**:
   - [Vilnius Voivodeship](/Vilnius_Voivodeship)
   - [Trakai Voivodeship](/Trakai_Voivodeship)
   - [Nowogródek Voivodeship](/Nowogr%C3%B3dek_Voivodeship_(1507-1795))
   - [Brest-Litovsk Voivodeship](/Brest-Litovsk_Voivodeship)
   - [Minsk Voivodeship](/Minsk_Voivodeship)
   - [Mścisław Voivodeship](/M%C5%9Bcis%C5%82aw_Voivodeship)
   - [Smolensk Voivodeship](/Smolensk_Voivodeship)
   - [Vitebsk Voivodeship](/Vitebsk_Voivodeship)
   - [Połock Voivodeship](/Po%C5%82ock_Voivodeship)

3. **Duchy of Livonia**:
   - [Wenden Voivodeship](/Wenden_Voivodeship) (1598–1620)
   - [Dorpat Voivodeship](/Dorpat_Voivodeship) (1598–1620)
   - [Parnawa Voivodeship](/Parnawa_Voivodeship) (1598–1620)
   - [Inflanty Voivodeship](/Inflanty_Voivodeship) (from the 1620s)

#### Congress Poland (1816–1837)

Following the [Congress of Vienna](/Congress_of_Vienna) in 1815, the [Congress Poland](/Congress_Poland) (a semi-autonomous state under the [Russian Empire](/Russian_Empire)) was divided into the following voivodeships:

- [Augustów Voivodeship](/August%C3%B3w_Voivodeship)
- [Kalisz Voivodeship](/Kalisz_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Kraków Voivodeship](/Krak%C3%B3w_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Lublin Voivodeship](/Lublin_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Masovian Voivodeship](/Masovian_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Płock Voivodeship](/P%C5%82ock_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Podlaskie Voivodeship](/Podlaskie_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))
- [Sandomierz Voivodeship](/Sandomierz_Voivodeship_(1816%E2%80%931837))

