- [Kielce Voivodeship](/Kielce_Voivodeship_(1919%E2%80%931939)) (*Województwo Kieleckie*)
- [Kraków Voivodeship](/Krak%C3%B3w_Voivodeship_(1919-1939)) (*Województwo Krakowskie*)
