- [Polesie Voivodeship](/Polesie_Voivodeship) (*Województwo Poleskie*)
- [Pomeranian Voivodeship](/Pomeranian_Voivodeship_(1919%E2%80%931939)) (*Województwo Pomorskie*)
- [Poznań Voivodeship](/Pozna%C5%84_Voivodeship_(1921%E2%80%931939)) (*Województwo Poznańskie*)
